114674e839d1c88e18bb","tid":666790,"uid":152500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  Rip"},{"pid":"7f62f43ced1e1e2d7905fa9f2ae5d07691ad486b","tid":666790,"uid":71887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:28:51.000Z","msg":"汗斑又稱為汗癬，它的特點是比膚色淡、<span style=\"color: red;\">脫皮及微癢</span>，有時會被誤以為白蝕。油性皮膚和出汗多的地方較常見，所以青少年身上，如<span style=\"color: red;\">胸前</span>、背脊等都有機會出現。<br />\n至於治療方面，病情輕的話，一般塗抹<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">抗真菌藥膏</span></strong>已可。「嚴重的人士可配合口服藥。很多人真菌反覆發作，主要是皮膚護理不當，如足部長期潮濕、流汗後不擦乾等。其實只要令皮膚保持乾爽，真<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>菌便難以生長。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_news/%E9%86%AB-for-essential-%E7%94%9F%E7%99%AC%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%9F%E6%AE%BA%E5%88%B0-%E5%8B%BF%E4%BA%82%E6%90%BD%E9%A1%9E%E5%9B%BA%E9%86%87%E8%97%A5%E8%86%8F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fmetro_news%2F%25E9%2586%25AB-for-essential-%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2599%25AC%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E5%258B%25BF%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%2590%25BD%25E9%25A1%259E%25E5%259B%25BA%25E9%2586%2587%25E8%2597%25A5%25E8%2586%258F%2F&d=71H6aUdLW1dRq8EZX0xA2S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=30b57178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_news/%E9%86%AB-for-essential-%E7%94%9F%E7%99%AC%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%9F%E6%AE%BA%E5%88%B0-%E5%8B%BF%E4%BA%82%E6%90%BD%E9%A1%9E%E5%9B%BA%E9%86%87%E8%97%A5%E8%86%8F/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇過篇野唔好搽類固醇 會愈搽愈衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1790e2722969886de2c214e939c8aff5720b47","tid":666790,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:31:40.000Z","msg":"無比膏<br />\n查完好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/